title: Eni says it's found 'supergiant' natural gas field off Egypt
text:
Mon, Aug 31, 2015, 7:08 AM AEST - Australia Markets open in 2 hrs 52 mins Eni says it's found 'supergiant' natural gas field off Egypt Italian energy giant Eni says it's found the largest-ever gas field in Mediterranean off Egypt Associated Press – 7 hours ago Recommend 
ROME (AP) -- The Italian energy company Eni says it has discovered a "supergiant" natural gas field off Egypt. 
A company statement on Sunday is calling it the "largest-ever" found in the Mediterranean Sea. 
Eni says after full development, the discovery will be able to ensure satisfying Egypt's natural gas demands "for decades." @y7finance on Twitter, become a fan on Facebook Australian market set to open higher AAP
